msgstr "例:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:29
msgid "ptool.fs.write"
msgstr "ptool.fs.write"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:31
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:31"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:33
msgid ""
"`ptool.fs.write(path, content)` writes a Lua string to a file as raw bytes, "
"overwriting existing contents."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.fs.write(path, content)` は Lua 文字列を生のバイト列としてファイルへ "
"書き込み、既存の内容を上書きします。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:36
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:36"
msgid "`path` (string, required): The file path."
msgstr "`path` (string, 必須): ファイルパス。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:37
msgid "`content` (string, required): The content to write."
msgstr "`content` (string, 必須): 書き込む内容。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:39
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:39"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "注意:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:41
msgid "`content` is written byte-for-byte."
msgstr "`content` は 1 バイトずつそのまま書き込まれます。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:42
msgid "Embedded NUL bytes and non-UTF-8 bytes are preserved."
msgstr "埋め込み NUL バイトや非 UTF-8 バイトも保持されます。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.5.0/lua-api/fs.md:44
